NAME
    Sys::RevoBackup - an rsync-based backup script

METHODS
  run
    Run the backups.

  vaults
    Return a list of all vaults (i.e. backup jobs).

CONFIGURATION
    Place the configuration inside /etc/revobackup/revobackup.conf

        <VTK>
            <RevoBackup>
                bank = /srv/backup/bank
                <Rotations>
                        daily = 10
                        weekly = 4
                        monthly = 12
                        yearly = 10
                </Rotations>
                <Vaults>
                        <test001>
                                source = /home/
                                description = Uhm
                                hardlink = 1
                                nocrossfs = 1
                        </test001>
                        <anotherhost>
                                source = anotherhost:/
                                description = Backup anotherhost
                        </anotherhost>
                </Vaults>
            </RevoBackup>
        </VTK>

NAME
    Sys::RevoBackup - Rsync based backup script

